 cfg‚Üź{projectPath}InitPackageConfig y;comments;msg;bool;list;varsList;projectConfig
‚ćĚ Initialise a package config namespace
‚ćĚ ‚ćĶ might be empty; then it is ignored.
‚ćĚ ‚ćĶ might be a namespace; then the content is copied into the config namespace after
‚ćĚ it got populated with defaults.
