 ‚ćĚcfg.exclude‚Üź''                ‚ćĚ Optional, therefore not included (for best compatability)  ‚ćĚTODO‚ćĚ Change before 1.0.0 is released
 ‚ćĚcomments,‚Üź'exclude' 'Optional. Name of one or more files/folders relative to "source" excluded from the package'
